import React from 'react';
import { 
    Box, 
    Typography, 
    Container, 
    Grid, 
    Card, 
    CardContent,
    Button,
    Paper,
    IconButton,
    Tooltip
} from '@mui/material';
import AddIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Add';
import CalendarTodayIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CalendarToday';
import SchoolIcon from '@mui/icons-material/School';
import AssignmentIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Assignment';
import SmartToyIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SmartToy';
import TimerIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Timer';

function Dashboard() {
    return (
        <Box
            sx={{
                minHeight: 'calc(100vh - 64px)',
                background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0F 0%, #1a1a1f 100%)',
                py: 4,
                position: 'relative',
                '&::before': {
                    content: '""',
                    position: 'absolute',
                    top: 0,
                    right: 0,
                    bottom: 0,
                    left: 0,
                    background: 'radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%)',
                    pointerEvents: 'none'
                }
            }}
        >
            <Container maxWidth="xl">
                {/* Welcome Section */}
                <Typography
                    variant="h3"
                    sx={{
                        mb: 4,
                        fontWeight: 700,
                        background: 'linear-gradient(45deg, #FFFFFF, #DC143C)',
                        WebkitBackgroundClip: 'text',
                        WebkitTextFillColor: 'transparent',
                        letterSpacing: '-0.02em',
                    }}
                >
                    Study Dashboard
                </Typography>

                {/* Main Features Grid */}
                <Grid container spacing={3}>
                    {/* Class Schedule Section */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                        <Card
                            sx={{
                                height: '100%',
                                background: 'rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.6)',
                                backdropFilter: 'blur(20px)',
                                borderRadius: 4,
                                border: '1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                            }}
                        >
                            <CardContent>
                                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 1 }}>
                                        <SchoolIcon sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }} />
                                        Class Schedule
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Tooltip title="Add Class">
                                        <IconButton sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }}>
                                            <AddIcon />
                                        </IconButton>
                                    </Tooltip>
                                </Box>
                                <Paper
                                    sx={{
                                        p: 3,
                                        background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)',
                                        borderRadius: 2,
                                        textAlign: 'center'
                                    }}
                                >
                                    <Typography color="text.secondary">
                                        Add your class schedule to get started
                                    </Typography>
                                </Paper>
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                    </Grid>

                    {/* Exam Dates Section */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                        <Card
                            sx={{
                                height: '100%',
                                background: 'rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.6)',
                                backdropFilter: 'blur(20px)',
                                borderRadius: 4,
                                border: '1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                            }}
                        >
                            <CardContent>
                                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 1 }}>
                                        <CalendarTodayIcon sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }} />
                                        Exam Dates
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Tooltip title="Add Exam">
                                        <IconButton sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }}>
                                            <AddIcon />
                                        </IconButton>
                                    </Tooltip>
                                </Box>
                                <Paper
                                    sx={{
                                        p: 3,
                                        background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)',
                                        borderRadius: 2,
                                        textAlign: 'center'
                                    }}
                                >
                                    <Typography color="text.secondary">
                                        Add your upcoming exams
                                    </Typography>
                                </Paper>
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                    </Grid>

                    {/* Tasks Section */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                        <Card
                            sx={{
                                height: '100%',
                                background: 'rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.6)',
                                backdropFilter: 'blur(20px)',
                                borderRadius: 4,
                                border: '1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                            }}
                        >
                            <CardContent>
                                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 1 }}>
                                        <AssignmentIcon sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }} />
                                        Tasks
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Tooltip title="Add Task">
                                        <IconButton sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }}>
                                            <AddIcon />
                                        </IconButton>
                                    </Tooltip>
                                </Box>
                                <Paper
                                    sx={{
                                        p: 3,
                                        background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)',
                                        borderRadius: 2,
                                        textAlign: 'center'
                                    }}
                                >
                                    <Typography color="text.secondary">
                                        Add tasks to optimize your study schedule
                                    </Typography>
                                </Paper>
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                    </Grid>

                    {/* AI Study Assistant Section */}
                    <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
                        <Card
                            sx={{
                                height: '100%',
                                background: 'rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.6)',
                                backdropFilter: 'blur(20px)',
                                borderRadius: 4,
                                border: '1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)',
                            }}
                        >
                            <CardContent>
                                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 1 }}>
                                        <SmartToyIcon sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }} />
                                        AI Study Assistant
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Tooltip title="Start Chat">
                                        <IconButton sx={{ color: '#DC143C' }}>
                                            <SmartToyIcon />
                                        </IconButton>
                                    </Tooltip>
                                </Box>
                                <Paper
                                    sx={{
                                        p: 3,
                                        background: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)',
                                        borderRadius: 2,
                                        textAlign: 'center'
                                    }}
                                >
                                    <Typography color="text.secondary">
                                        Get personalized study plans and assistance
                                    </Typography>
                                </Paper>
                            </CardContent>
                        </Card>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Container>
        </Box>
    );
}

export default Dashboard;
